SRTMconv
--------

Convert SRTM files to VisuGps format.

This application has been developped with Ultimate++ <http://www.ultimatepp.org/>

SRTM files can be found at <http://srtm.csi.cgiar.org/index.asp>

Author
------

Victor Berchet


VisuGPS SRTM file format
------------------------

VisuGps expect SRTM data in the following format:
filename: strm3_<low left corner longitude>_<low left corner latitude>.strmb
data: 6000*6000 points (5*5 degree). Each point being a single byte = elevation in meter / 20.
	
